{"id":692431,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/692431.html","date":"2023-01-29T06:30:53Z","modified":"2023-01-29T06:05:24Z","title":"in ran｜但是春联不只一种颜色","content":"<div style=\"width:42%;float:right;padding-left:20px;\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\"><br />\n<strong>标题：</strong>但是春联不只一种颜色<br />\n<strong>作者：</strong>in ran<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/XQeYHUe31qAvzXV0FrXlMQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">微信公众号“in ran”</a><br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2023.1.27<br />\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/新冠疫情\" target=\"_blank\">新冠疫情</a><br><br />\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E8%AF%9D%E8%AF%AD%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">话语馆</a><br><br />\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。<br />\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p>在老家如果家里有直系亲属过世，以前的习俗是三年之内不能贴红色春联：第一年贴黄色春联，第二年贴绿色或蓝色，第三年紫色。而现在基本上只有第一年不贴红色春联，贴黄色、绿色或者蓝色的都可以，到第二年就恢复红色春联。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa615681.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>这次回老家乡镇过年，大年三十那晚吃过年夜饭后，我去街上散了会步。从地图上估算走了3000米，大概经过1300户临街的人家，其中43家没有贴红色春联。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa625e1c.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>镇上有一条400米长的老街，房屋大多还是三四十年前的面貌。这条街共7家没有贴红色春联，平均下来每走50多米就有一家。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa652943.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>北大街的这5家里有3家不是红色春联。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa679755.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa6a7f54.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa6d12d6.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa703fa8.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p>另外看到好几处相邻的两家都不是红色春联。</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa72d313.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa753474.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa7839a6.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa7a734b.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa7d53aa.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa804bf0.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa831eed.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60aa85d310.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60ad90dbe4.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2023/01/post-692431-63d60ad932a6c.png\" alt=\"image\" /></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese